  "3301010": {
    "name": "Den-Den: Tokyo Horror",
    "steam_appid": 3301010,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Den-Den: Tokyo Horror 是一款开放世界恐怖 RPG，每一个选择都承载着生命的重量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日本出生率早已崩溃。老龄人口是年轻人的三倍以上，东京正在缓缓死去。 残酷的地缘政治封锁切断了食物、药品和电力供给，社会正在分崩离析，暴力犯罪激增。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是护理人员。 你的任务：让负责照顾的被遗忘老人活过七个夜晚。 残酷的现实是——物资永远不够。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第七个黎明到来时，还剩多少人活着？ 你还敢直视镜子里的自己吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 Den-Den: Tokyo Horror。 这个故事没有圆满结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/3d71d2e120c3f8323802ea517889b3b0.poster.avif?t=1765375798\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/3d71d2e120c3f8323802ea517889b3b0.webm?t=1765375798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/3d71d2e120c3f8323802ea517889b3b0.mp4?t=1765375798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特性</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不断崩坏的巨型反应式开放世界东京中熬过七个无情的夜晚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每过去一夜，城市便陷入更深的混乱。时间永不停止，每个选择都有后果</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理有限物资，在废墟中搜刮一切能让你再活一晚的东西</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用遍布城市的回收机把垃圾变成救命宝物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入噩梦般的养老设施，照顾你负责的被遗弃老人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集并装备强大的御守，获得超自然加护（有时也会带来诅咒）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用菜刀、电击枪、黑市手枪等临时武器战斗或逃跑</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >行动拥有永久后果，游戏内每个角色都可能因你而死</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Scavenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >翻遍废弃公寓、溢出的垃圾箱、黑暗小巷，只为找到能多活一晚的东西——食物、止痛药、电池、子弹……或者一无所获。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/8943a4e4cd759db05c02a391ad33015c.poster.avif?t=1765375798\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/8943a4e4cd759db05c02a391ad33015c.webm?t=1765375798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/8943a4e4cd759db05c02a391ad33015c.mp4?t=1765375798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Discover</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对话、倾听、撒谎、威胁或安慰。每段对话都会分支，每段关系都可能救你或毁掉你想保护的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/2117e3547f4bf8e11fcc095990f9b7ce.poster.avif?t=1765375798\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/2117e3547f4bf8e11fcc095990f9b7ce.webm?t=1765375798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/2117e3547f4bf8e11fcc095990f9b7ce.mp4?t=1765375798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight or Flight</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绝望的市民、暴力罪犯以及更可怕的东西在街头游荡。挥舞生锈的菜刀、颤抖着开枪、用电击枪麻痹敌人，或者只是逃跑——不惜一切活到天亮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/7c15bd30f7fa7fa45dec5deccc966081.poster.avif?t=1765375798\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/7c15bd30f7fa7fa45dec5deccc966081.webm?t=1765375798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/7c15bd30f7fa7fa45dec5deccc966081.mp4?t=1765375798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fear</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城市最黑暗的角落里，某种邪恶之物已经苏醒。 它以疏忽、後悔和错误决定为食。 如果你犯下太多错误……它会找上你，以及你没能守护的所有人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/0bc2d5ac1bd5b88870b53f3d05f68756.poster.avif?t=1765375798\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/0bc2d5ac1bd5b88870b53f3d05f68756.webm?t=1765375798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301010/extras/0bc2d5ac1bd5b88870b53f3d05f68756.mp4?t=1765375798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
